{"tid":1882544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反對政府改口免費包機載鑽石公主號滯留港人 國泰疑招「死士」接客","createTime":"2020-02-16T10:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T11:41:12.000Z","uid":47643,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b5db0341f69a5194618cd8534c497e8f271b0e1f","tid":1882544,"uid":47643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:24:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200216/ZDY4KRCBV7HSOTCET74OLXBPU4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200216%2FZDY4KRCBV7HSOTCET74OLXBPU4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfboE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=085ee78f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200216%2FZDY4KRCBV7HSOTCET74OLXBPU4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&h=8ad57de6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200216/ZDY4KRCBV7HSOTCET74OLXBPU4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link</a><br />\n<br />\n有傳港府正準備於下周四（20日）包機送船上港人回港。有空中服務員向《蘋果》透露，數名國泰的空姐空少已準備到該兩班特別航班服務，全部屬自願，希望協助船上港人回港。所有員工會穿上「生化衫」，亦不會與乘客有正面接觸，「只會arm door（為機艙門設置為緊急模式）同埋evacuation duties（疏散程序）」。<br />\n<br />\n滯留船上的港人袁小姐對政府安排大感不滿，斥返港後再隔離14日「唔make sense 」，「依家講緊最長潛伏期都係24日，特區政府要我地total隔離28日？」她續說，「人哋日本政府都話測試無問題，我哋就可以上岸，即係我哋前後隔離左14日仲要過埋測試無事先返到香港，仲clean過正常人！憑乜要我哋返去又隔多14日？！」她又問，為何內地返港人士可以家居隔離，但他們就要入住隔離營。她希望政府可以於18日或之前包機送他們返港，她與家人願意接受家居隔離多14日，「我哋1月25號開始已經無返過屋企，身心都已經累。」<br />\n<br />\n根本而家成船都係毒, 放班喪屍返來攬炒? <br />\n支持機師空姐擺工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53df66fac9f15f53a909c83c134c07ee21eddbc1","tid":1882544,"uid":40908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"仲講罷工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算吧啦"},{"pid":"0a42457e577c9ee2402d41ece61f680516c899d7","tid":1882544,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"點解支那蝗唔洗入隔籬營"},{"pid":"9e2523d53bb835ec9ee279d8d826a7a70ecf7bab","tid":1882544,"uid":150014,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:41:20.000Z","msg":"架郵輪日日有班人確診<br />\n上面邊個可以保證自己一定無中招？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0558fdaea39b545ff72ca47d6a4f3060363271","tid":1882544,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"由佢地死好過啦, 送班仆街返黎播毒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db92387bc5ccb2b75bef9227fbd81785a6c83fad","tid":1882544,"uid":241399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"咁袁小姐都係繼續留係日本啦<br />\n宜家美國都頂日本唔順話佢地隔離得太 hea<br />\n攪到日日隻船都有新 case<br />\n所以係隻船隔離都唔保證無事"},{"pid":"f1026d36db5c20191a622e12690b8a38aee0f535","tid":1882544,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"解決方法就係支那豬通通強制隔離14日<br />\n呢班野就唔使再包機番黎<br />\n簡直完美"},{"pid":"ac5e0158423bae055a2ba26e136156edadb489f8","tid":1882544,"uid":47643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"家居隔離, 樓上樓下既多得佢唔少"},{"pid":"be14f42a885065c3b8099ff2ec468f16f9711b3e","tid":1882544,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:54:12.000Z","msg":"咁咪咪撚返嚟囉 繼續留喺隻船度"},{"pid":"772a644a123f05a51b207d979590526b611f618f","tid":1882544,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"53df66fac9f15f53a909c83c134c07ee21eddbc1","tid":1882544,"uid":40908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"仲講罷工？<img src=\"/assets/